</td></tr></table>
<hr />
<p>Six forms of <a href="/wiki/Pikachu_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Pikachu (Pokémon)">Pikachu</a>, each wearing one of Ash's six hats between the original series and the <i>Sun &amp; Moon</i> series, will be distributed to moviegoers who pre-order tickets to the <a href="/wiki/M20" title="M20">20th Pokémon movie</a>. A seventh form, wearing Ash's hat from <i><a href="/wiki/M20" title="M20">I Choose You!</a></i>, will be distributed in <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Ultra_Sun_and_Ultra_Moon" title="Pokémon Ultra Sun and Ultra Moon">Pokémon Ultra Sun and Ultra Moon</a> via a special <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Ga-Ol%C3%A9" title="Pokémon Ga-Olé">Pokémon Ga-Olé</a> disc.
<br clear="all" />
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Side_series">Side series</span></h3>
<table style="margin:auto; background: #FAFFF4; border: 2px solid #F08030; border-radius: 30px; -moz-border-radius: 30px; -webkit-border-radius: 30px; -khtml-border-radius: 30px; -icab-border-radius: 30px; -o-border-radius: 30px;">

<tr>
<td style="text-align:center; background:#F5AC78; padding: 10px; border-radius: 50px; -moz-border-radius: 50px; -webkit-border-radius: 50px; -khtml-border-radius: 50px; -icab-border-radius: 50px; -o-border-radius: 50px;"> <a href="/wiki/File:Spr_1g_006.png" class="image"><img alt="Spr 1g 006.png" src="//cdn.bulbagarden.net/upload/5/59/Spr_1g_006.png" width="56" height="56" /></a>
</td>
<td> <b>The picture used in this section is unsatisfactory.</b><br /><small>Reason: The hat itself is too far away.</small><br />Please feel free to replace it so it conforms to Bulbapedia conventions.
</td></tr></table><div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:202px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ash_hat_Hey_You_Pikachu.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="//cdn.bulbagarden.net/upload/thumb/6/63/Ash_hat_Hey_You_Pikachu.png/200px-Ash_hat_Hey_You_Pikachu.png" width="200" height="142" class="thumbimage" srcset="//cdn.bulbagarden.net/upload/thumb/6/63/Ash_hat_Hey_You_Pikachu.png/300px-Ash_hat_Hey_You_Pikachu.png 1.5x, //cdn.bulbagarden.net/upload/thumb/6/63/Ash_hat_Hey_You_Pikachu.png/400px-Ash_hat_Hey_You_Pikachu.png 2x" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Ash_hat_Hey_You_Pikachu.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Ash's hat in Hey You, Pikachu</div></div></div>
<p>In <a href="/wiki/Hey_You,_Pikachu!" title="Hey You, Pikachu!">Hey You, Pikachu!</a>, the original hat, along with the rest of the outfit, can be seen hanging on a coat rack in the player's bedroom. Pikachu uses the hat in "The Piñata Game" to cover his eyes.
<br clear="all" />
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Trivia">Trivia</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:162px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ash_hat_OS_concept_art.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//cdn.bulbagarden.net/upload/thumb/8/87/Ash_hat_OS_concept_art.jpg/160px-Ash_hat_OS_concept_art.jpg" width="160" height="246" class="thumbimage" srcset="//cdn.bulbagarden.net/upload/thumb/8/87/Ash_hat_OS_concept_art.jpg/240px-Ash_hat_OS_concept_art.jpg 1.5x, //cdn.bulbagarden.net/upload/thumb/8/87/Ash_hat_OS_concept_art.jpg/320px-Ash_hat_OS_concept_art.jpg 2x" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Ash_hat_OS_concept_art.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Concept art of the Pokémon League Expo hat</div></div></div>
<ul><li> Early concept art of the Pokémon League Expo hat shows similarities with <a href="/wiki/Red_(game)" title="Red (game)">Red</a>'s hat in his original design from <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Red_and_Green_Versions" title="Pokémon Red and Green Versions">Pokémon Red and Green</a>.</li>
<li> In <i><a href="/wiki/EP037" title="EP037">Ditto's Mysterious Mansion</a></i>, <a href="/wiki/Duplica" title="Duplica">Duplica</a> is shown to own a hat that appears identical to Ash's Pokémon League Expo hat.</li>
<li> According to the <i><a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Visual_Guide" title="Pokémon Visual Guide">Pokémon Visual Guide</a></i> and its sequels, Ash obtained the Pokémon League Expo hat by mailing in cereal box tops. In <i><a href="/wiki/EP025" title="EP025">Primeape Goes Bananas</a></i>, Ash says he had to send in a million "postcards" in order to obtain it.</li></ul>
<p><br clear="all" />
</p>
